title: 'Jet black jeans and looks awesome'
body: Please don't worry about the reviews in which people are claiming that this will fade away after 2-3 washes or that the fit is bad. I ordered the same jeans 2-3 years ago and I still use it for both formal and casual occasions. The colour hasn't faded at all and it's still high utility and high comfort. This is a skinny tapered fit and yes make sure your thighs are not too broad in case if you are a bit on the heavier side. Its a long lasting, high quality jean and now I have two of it.
